r waste within 10 working days if you have questions about this form submission please e mail to tom finnigan or call ext 3 8034 empty container decision tree request for analysis of unknown chemical waste this form is to be used for disposal of an unknown chemical waste please provide as much information about the material as possible it is very costly to analyze and dispose of materials that cannot be identified research equipment disposal and release to surplus list of non hazardous chemical wastes list of acutely hazardous wastes list of extremely hazardous wastes hazard category classifications for chemical waste laboratory chemical waste guidelines chemical waste and emergency response program staff back to environmental programs home page
